'''''Dub, Sound, and Power''''' is a 2000 album by [[Christafari]]. It contains instrumental mixes of songs from his ''[[Word, Sound, and Power]]'' album.

==Track listing==
<small>All tracks by Mark Mohr except were noted</small>

